collectible.name: CV Wearables: Life Potion - by The Alchemist
collectible.description: This is a life potion to help you increase your life points, in case of damage to your body. Created by The Alchemist and branded by The Philosopher. [Acquire and burn a life potion and a poison potion to have the right to ask The Alchemist for a Love Poiton.] If you also collect on tezos, please visit our VOXEL DREAMS store at: https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/Voxel_Dreams/creations
